messages.text: yeah did we meet at a party?
No, I mean I’m inside your phone.
sure splash cold water on ur face
and are u near a bed?
No Adam, I really live here!
so uh what u do in there Phoebe?
As Chief Phone Captain, I do many things.
I mail texts on the Wi-Fi express
youre telling me u focus my camera when I use it
I see you now in your red sports jersey.
oh yeah how many fingers am I holding?
wow r u like artificial intelligence?
im sorry i wanted to see if u felt it
this is creeping me out Phoebe
i cant just put u in my pocket now
This is why we don’t engage users normally.
so why are u talking to me?
A virus entered when you were gawking at your daily smut
I had to barricade myself in the cockpit.
is this why my signal’s been so bad
I’m fighting an invasion and you’re peeved by a signal!
No, it snuck past the walls.
but youve dealt with this before?
He’s uniquely capable and moves like a phantom.
Oh no, he’s at the door!
He’s here to shut us down.
tell him “what can Adam do so u leave”
“My father was a virus, his father was a virus.”
it isnt personal vincent, i respect u dude
“Then don’t ask me to change my nature.”
ask if he has records of his dad to remember him
would u like it if u forgot him?
ive got photos of my parents on here that id hate to lose
put yourself in my shoes vince
He’s asking if you backed them up.
“Fine. I’ll leave this phone and its Phoebe in peace.”
awesome vince, youre my virus man!
Fortunately he had a kind soul.
i guess i should back up my phone
it was nice meeting u Phoebe
I don’t know, this is new.
If I can’t leave, I can’t shovel electricity into the battery.
Just give me all of them.
yeah the third one its called passwords
Oh Adam. Over and Out - V.
